>phillip chia wrote:
> I want to use the digital port as an  analog port input.  How should I
> convert the digital port to analog in using programming way ?

 Just thought I would add that it *is* possible (if a bit slow) to read an
analog signal w/ a digital port by timing the decay of the signal thru a RC
circuit...not a particularly precise method, either.


